@startuml
!include ../style.puml

participant Client
participant "Coordinator" as Coord
participant "Participant" as Part

'[step]
Client -> Coord: 1. BeginTransaction
Coord --> Client: OK

'[step]
Client -> Part: 2. WriteIntent(key)
Part --> Client: OK

'[step]
Client -> Coord: 3. CommitTransaction
note right of Coord
  **Fast Commit**
  Transaction is legally committed
  once the status flips in memory!
end note
Coord -> Coord: Set TxnStatus = COMMITTED
Coord --> Client: 4. OK (Success!)

'[step]
note over Coord, Part
  **Asynchronous Resolve**
  Coordinator tells Participants to cleanup.
  Client does NOT wait for this!
end note
Coord -> Part: 5. ResolveRequest(key)
Part -> Part: Move Intent to CommittedStore
@enduml
